{"tid":1357184,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［嚴重警告］唔好再指責同伴關注元朗","createTime":"2019-07-23T16:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T16:57:37.000Z","uid":108687,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4aefd178454b6f6029b5563aad56e0b34573fc53","tid":1357184,"uid":108687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:16:29.000Z","msg":"1. 革命 / 反抗 / 抗爭進行中，元朗係事態嘅最新發展，係嚴重嘅警察包庇黑社會暴力份子，軍警政權嘅鎮壓外判，係暴政打壓示威者嘅<strong>最新手段</strong>，不可能唔關注。<br />\n<br />\n2. 任何有血性嘅人因為元朗嘅事都會義憤填膺。<br />\n<br />\n3. 關於新發展、新手段，我哋必須有人討論如何應對。舊有問題一樣要有人討論如何應對。<strong>港島大型對陣戰必須要繼續吸收經驗，繼續進步。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家識諗，不贅。"},{"pid":"6a0fba717e0c10480597950cf89186a65add727c","tid":1357184,"uid":108687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:17:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc9c7a6a72e7b98bb5949af6420352bc886c9685","tid":1357184,"uid":108687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:19:33.000Z","msg":"我覺得開始有另類人士上黎連登搞分化/或真心過左龍<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dpfKdS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dpfKdS</a><br />\n<br />\n唔明點解有手足成日覺得理元朗等如放棄主線<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1355260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1355260</a>"},{"pid":"4b8d203a57718e4a901aecdade5a0042374b9034","tid":1357184,"uid":108687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-2